          "1a_reason": "Music features are identified per section and a few count-level correspondences are clear (e.g., drum entry on 3, guitar entry on 5, cowbell emphasis in choruses, final hit on 72). However, most claims like “hits snare on 2&4” are not consistently mapped to exact counts within each 8-count phrase, and several instrument-response links remain general rather than beat-specific.",
